OL,3,CBlood victim's daughter criticises
OL,4,Cappointment of new advisor on
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FProfessor Sir Jonathan Montgomery has
OL,8,Fnow been appointed to chair a group of
OL,9,Fexperts offering "technical advice" to
OL,10,Fthe compensation talks, but his links
OL,11,Fto a pharmaceutical firm and NHS trust
OL,12,Fimplicated in the scandal have been
OL,13,Fhighlighted by campaigners as being
OL,14,Fpotentially problematic.
OL,16,FFor decades, Jonathan Colam-French,
OL,17,Fwho lives near Spilsby in , had no
OL,18,Fidea he had been infected with
OL,19,Fhepatitis C.
