OL,7,F"I was infected so young that my
OL,8,Fnormal was my normal," he said. "The
OL,9,Fbest years of my life were spent
OL,10,Ffeeling ill."
OL,12,FAt the age of 12 he was treated for a
OL,13,Fbruised finger, but he was in his 30s
OL,14,Fby the time he was told he - like
OL,15,Fthousands of others - had been given
OL,16,Fcontaminated blood to do so.
OL,18,FHe has since joined the fight for
OL,19,Fcompensation, but says the interests
OL,20,Fof victims like him still are not
OL,21,Fbeing put first.
