OL,7,F"I can't see an end in sight. It feels
OL,8,Flike they're going to keep dragging
OL,9,Fthis on," said Mr Colam-French.
OL,11,F"I had 20 years with my liver being
OL,12,Fdamaged on a daily basis. I know
OL,13,Fthat's going to impact on the amount
OL,14,Fof time I've got available and I don't
OL,15,Fwant to waste it."
OL,17,FIn the 1970s and 80s, blood product
OL,18,F'Factor 8' was sourced from high risk
OL,19,Fdonors in America like prisoners, drug
OL,20,Faddicts and sex workers to treat
OL,21,Fpatients in the UK.
