OL,7,FHe is also chair of Oxford University
OL,8,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust, whose
OL,9,Fhaemophilia unit was criticised during
OL,10,Fthe public inquiry, and he has links
OL,11,Fto pharmaceutical firm Bayer which
OL,12,Fmade and supplied infected blood
OL,13,Fproducts.
OL,15,F"It's not ethical, it's a complete
OL,16,Fconflict of interest," said Sarah
OL,17,FDorricott from , whose father, Mike,
OL,18,Fwas infected when he was 15 years old.
