OL,7,F"It would be like hiring someone from
OL,8,FFujitsu to advise the government on
OL,9,Fcompensation for the Post Office
OL,10,Fscandal.
OL,12,F"It's completely inappropriate."
OL,14,FMr Dorricott contracted hepatitis C
OL,15,Fafter undergoing routine dental
OL,16,Fsurgery.
OL,18,FIt later caused liver cancer which he
OL,19,Fdied from in 2015 before being awarded
OL,20,Fany compensation.
