OL,7,F"My dad was such an avid campaigner
OL,8,Fand had such a sense of justice he
OL,9,Fwould be furious," said Ms Dorricott.
OL,11,F"I don't think the government have
OL,12,Fdone this ignorantly, I think they're
OL,13,Fplaying games with us.
OL,15,F"I'm shaking because I'm that angry,"
OL,16,Fshe said.
OL,18,F"Why can't we be shown some empathy
OL,19,Fcare and attention? It's insulting."
