OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Sir Jonathan is an
OL,9,Fexperienced healthcare law scholar who
OL,10,Fhas played a leading role in UK public
OL,11,Fbioethics.
OL,13,F"Last year he ceased to be a member of
OL,14,Fthe Bayer Bioethics Council, which is
